text: Chathura Lakshan (born 30 March 1995) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Galle Cricket Club in the 2017–18 SLC Twenty20 Tournament on 24 February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Galle Cricket Club cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Galle
